Please include helpful information to questions we may have such as:
1. Is the song/video a single? Is there a radio clean version available?
2. Is the song a part of an upcoming album/mixtape? If so what is the title & release date?
3. Is there a related video available for the single via Vimeo or Youtube?
4. Does the artist have a short yet effective bio available? Where from? What record label etc?
5. Does the artist or producer have a twitter, facebook, itunes buy links, and or website?
